          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1702404310534-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>koftas</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Once the koftas have browned, transfer them to a plate and set aside, these will finish cooking in the sauce later</p><p>Reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702404324281-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702404324281-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702404324281-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702404324281-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702404324281-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the koftas are cooking, crush <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>cardamom pods </strong>open by squashing them with the side of a knife (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Discard the <strong>outer green pods</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> and <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> in 120ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1702404335148-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1702404335148-x400.jpg",
