          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1702404357766-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Bangladeshi-style lean beef kofta curry</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>fragrant rice </strong>to the side, discard the <strong>cardamom pods </strong>and <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
